last_episode_to_air.name: Go Getters Gonna Go Getcha
last_episode_to_air.overview: Krystal helps Judd out of a jam. Cody finds himself pulled in two directions. Bets puts her foot down. Buck and Pat see an opportunity. Season finale.

name: On Becoming a God in Central Florida
original_name: On Becoming a God in Central Florida
overview: In the early 1990s, a recently widowed, impoverished Orlando water park employee schemes and cons her way up the ranks of the multi-billion dollar pyramid scheme which ruined her financially in the first place.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: When an elaborate, cultish, multi-billion-dollar pyramid scheme drives her family to ruin, Krystal Stubbs takes destiny into her own hands. In order to make a better life for herself and her family, this minimum-wage water park employee dives head first into the scheme, determined to come out on top.

episodes.name: The Stinker Thinker
episodes.overview: Krystal Stubbs doubles down on her husband's dreams while he wrestles with leaving his J-O-B. Cody loses a friend, but meets his hero.

episodes.name: The Gloomy-Zoomies
episodes.overview: Krystal networks her way into an opportunity in the beauty pageant industry. Cody tries to be his own workhorse. Ernie builds a time capsule.

episodes.name: A Positive Spin!
episodes.overview: Krystal and Cody throw a rally. Ernie tries to connect with his son. Stan finds a new supplier for the water park.

episodes.name: Manifest Destinee
episodes.overview: Stricken with a bird disease, Krystal goes on an odyssey. A collection of vintage motivational tapes just might change Cody’s destiny. Ernie tries recruiting.

episodes.name: Many Masters
episodes.overview: Obie and Louise Garbeau host a lavish motivational retreat at Paradise Cay for Washington-level entrepreneurs.

episodes.name: American Merchandise
episodes.overview: Krystal rubs elbows with the upper crust. Cody makes a surprising business proposal. Ernie finds his rhythm as a recruiter and celebrates with pizza.

episodes.name: Flint Glass
episodes.overview: Krystal takes initiative and drums up some press for her business. Cody finally gets some one-on-one coaching. Bets isn’t sure about FAM.

episodes.name: Birthday Party
episodes.overview: Krystal loses her job, but gets a personal invitation to Paradise Cay. Roger trains Cody in security protocols. Ernie and Bets cha-cha.

episodes.name: Wham Bam Thank You FAM
episodes.overview: The Orlando FAM community braces for the Wham Bam Thank You FAM 37th Anniversary Jam. Krystal’s loyalties are tested. Obie opens his heart to some orphans. Harold says a cuss word.

episodes.name: Go Getters Gonna Go Getcha
episodes.overview: Krystal helps Judd out of a jam. Cody finds himself pulled in two directions. Bets puts her foot down. Buck and Pat see an opportunity. Season finale.
